The paper discusses a meta-heuristic optimization algorithm for solving numerical optimization problems. This falls under the category of machine learning and optimization, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. The most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it specifically deals with optimization algorithms. The next likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as they also cover optimization algorithms and their applications. The paper also involves experiments and comparisons with other algorithms, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
